title: Delia Derbyshire Collection
description:
These are files originally downloaded from delia-derbyshire.net as ogg vorbis files. I converted them to mp3s using Audacity. They are stereo and 320kbps. They are categorized by year as according to the site. I have also zipped them into a RAR file.

I am a musician and a big fan of Delia Derbyshire. She was a pioneer in electronic music and paved the way for electronic musicians and sampling artists of today. I hope these rare gems will forever be on the internet so many people can appreciate this woman's brilliance.

Please check out the site http://delia-derbyshire.net/ for everything about this amazing woman. Long live Delia!
